data.description: Welcome to your new home that sits on beautiful Lake Bonny with spectacular sunsets! Enjoy watching the wonderful fireworks while swimming in your very own refreshing pool. Minutes away from Downtown Lakeland, this spacious home has a HUGE living area for hosting and family gatherings with a wonderful view of of the lake. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home sits on nearly 3/4 of an acre, totaling over 1,800 square feet with 70 feet of lake frontage! Bring all offers and get ready to see what Florida Living is all about.
